				<h1 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">Today in Small Business: Paternity Leave</h1>
		<div class="story-meta-footer">
			<address class="byline author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
				By Gene Marks			</address>
			<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2014-11-07T17:26:24+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">November 7, 2014 12:26 pm</time>
			<!-- date updated --><span class="visually-hidden updated">November 7, 2014 12:26 pm</span><button class="button comments-button  theme-kicker" data-skip-to-para-id="">
</button>
		</div>
			</header>
		<div class="entry-content"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/11/07/today-in-small-business-paternity-leave/" data-title="Today in Small Business: Paternity Leave" data-description="The economy is producing steady gains on jobs. Oyster farming is booming. And here&#039;s why the new soda tax in Berkeley, Calif., may not reduce obesity.">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
				<div id="MiddleLeft" class="ad middle-left-ad nocontent robots-nocontent"></div>
				</div><div class="inlineModule"><div class="entry"><h6 class="kicker"><a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/category/dashboard/">Dashboard</a></h6><p class="summary">A daily roundup of small-business developments.</p></div></div>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>The Economy</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Jobs data show <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/11/08/business/jobs-numbers-for-october-2014-reported-by-labor-department.html">steady gains</a> (even as voters signal anxiety).</li>
<li>The Federal Reserve <a href="//www.reuters.com/article/2014/11/07/us-usa-fed-mester-rates-idUSKBN0IR05N20141107?f">is likely to raise</a> interest rates next year.</li>
<li>Positive <a href="//www.foxbusiness.com/markets/2014/11/06/positive-economic-sentiment-keeps-stocks-at-record-levels/">economic sentiment</a> is keeping stocks at record levels.</li>
<li>Restaurant industry <a href="//nrn.com/black-box/report-october-same-store-sales-signal-promising-4q">performance improved</a> in October, surpassing Septemberâs strong results.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Taxes</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Here&#8217;s why the <a href="//www.vox.com/2014/11/7/7159887/soda-tax-berkeley-weight-loss-obesity">new soda tax</a> in Berkeley, Calif., won&#8217;t reduce obesity.</li>
<li>Here is why a grand bargain on tax reform <a href="//www.inc.com/jeremy-quittner/why-a-grand-bargain-on-taxes-is-likely.html">has as chance</a> to pass before President Obama&#8217;s term expires.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Employees</strong></p>
<ul>
<ul>
<li><a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/11/09/upshot/paternity-leave-the-rewards-and-the-remaining-stigma.html">Men who take paternity leave</a> are facing many of the career challenges women have long faced.</li>
<li>Expedia&#8217;s <a href="//www.hospitalitynet.org/news/4067677.html">Vacation Deprivation Study</a> finds that American and Asian workers lag Europeans in taking vacations.</li>
</ul>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span id="more-90004"></span></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Start-Up</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Mark Pincus, the former Zynga chief executive, <a href="//www.fastcompany.com/3038171/most-creative-people/zynga-founder-mark-pincus-launches-a-startup-factory">starts a</a> San Francisco-based quasi-incubator.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Social Media</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Facebook will be <a href="//www.pcworld.com/article/2844852/facebook-will-be-mostly-video-in-5-years-zuckerberg-says.html#tk.rss_all">mostly video</a> in five years, a chief executive asserts.</li>
<li>This flow chart can <a href="//articles.bplans.com/social-media-response-flow-chart/?ut">help you determine</a> how to respond to a social media mention.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Cash Flow</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Someone paid $300,000 <a href="//gawker.com/someone-paid-300-000-to-have-lasagna-at-bruce-springst-1655734313">to eat lasagna</a> at Bruce Springsteen&#8217;s house.</li>
<li>Here are 10 <a href="//startupcollective.com/10-often-overlooked-bookkeeping-strategies/">overlooked bookkeeping</a>Â  strategies</li>
<li>Jay Z likes <a href="//money.cnn.com/2014/11/06/luxury/jay-z-champagne-beyonce/index.html">his $300 champagne</a> so much he bought the company.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Finance</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The Small Business Administration <a href="//www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/sba-hits-another-lending-record-in-fy-2014-281767141.html">hits a lending record</a>.</li>
<li>Here are six <a href="//www.hypebot.com/hypebot/2014/11/6-ways-to-reach-your-kickstarter-goal.html">ways to reach</a> your Kickstarter goal.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Management</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Microsoft is changing its strategy and <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/11/07/technology/microsoft-to-give-away-mobile-version-of-office-software.html">giving away the mobile edition</a> of Office.</li>
<li>Can&#8217;t focus? <a href="//www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/11/06/office-paint-colors-best-for-focus_n_5998532.html">Your office paint</a> color might be to blame.</li>
<li>New research explains how <a href="https://hbr.org/2014/11/research-how-female-ceos-actually-get-to-the-top/">female chief executives</a> get to the top.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Online</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Hackers <a href="//www.foxbusiness.com/markets/2014/11/06/home-depot-says-hackers-break-into-system-via-third-party-vendor-steal-53m/">break into</a> Home Depotâs system and steal email addresses.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Marketing</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>If you want customers <a href="//www.businessinsider.com/chart-of-the-day-retailers-should-use-email-for-coupons-2014-11">to take advantage</a> of deals and coupons, use email.</li>
<li>Living Social is <a href="//www.washingtonpost.com/business/capitalbusiness/livingsocial-to-eliminate-400-jobs-as-the-deals-company-charts-a-new-path-forward/2014/11/05/11ee8c50-650a-11e4-836c-83bc4f26eb67_story.html?wpisrc=nl-headlines&amp;wpmm=1">eliminating 400 jobs</a> and looking for a new path forward.</li>
<li>The former Apple and Pepsi chief executive John Sculley <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SqH7u5WQ7gE&amp;feature=youtu.be">reflects on</a> the ad campaign that made Coke &#8220;go ballistic.&#8221;</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Diversity</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>In New Jersey, a lesbian business owner <a href="//www.theblaze.com/stories/2014/11/05/why-a-lesbian-business-owner-is-standing-up-for-a-christian-printers-right-to-refuse-making-t-shirts-for-a-gay-pride-event/">is standing up</a> for a Christian printerâs right to refuse making t-shirts for a gay pride event.</li>
<li>In Northern Ireland, a Christian bakery owner <a href="//news.sky.com/story/1367948/bakery-faces-legal-action-over-gay-rights-cake?u">says he faces</a> legal action unless he pays compensation for refusing to make a pro-gay marriage cake.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Around the Country</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A Broadway institution <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/11/07/nyregion/cafe-edison-a-longtime-broadway-hangout-is-closing.html">announces it is closing</a>.</li>
<li>In Maryland, <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/11/07/us/a-new-bounty-of-oysters-in-maryland-but-there-is-a-snag.html">oyster farming is booming</a> but creating conflict.</li>
<li>A Springfield, Mo., <a href="//www.csmonitor.com/World/Making-a-difference/Change-Agent/2014/1106/A-chocolate-factory-with-a-higher-purpose">chocolate factory</a> has a higher purpose.</li>
<li>Dallas <a href="//www.bizjournals.com/dallas/news/2014/11/06/dallas-ranks-first-for-small-business-job-growth.html">ranks first</a> for small-business job growth in October.</li>
<li>City leaders in Nevada City voted to <a href="//sacramento.cbslocal.com/2014/11/05/nevada-city-business-owners-fight-to-keep-lights-on-after-city-council-decision/">turn off the lights</a> in the downtown historic district ten months of the year, a move thatâs upsetting business owners.</li>
<li>Manufacturing <a href="//www.industryweek.com/expansion-management/why-does-manufacturing-have-stronghold-san-antonio">has a stronghold</a> in San Antonio.</li>
<li>It&#8217;s not just tech &#8212; a <a href="//money.cnn.com/2014/11/06/smallbusiness/san-francisco-manufacturing/index.html?sect">pint of beer</a> is also vital to San Francisco&#8217;s growth.</li>
<li>A new <a href="//www.capitolhilltimes.com/2014/11/murray-launches-restaurant-success-initiative/?u">initiative</a> in Washington State is aimed at providing better resources for restaurant start-ups.</li>
<li>A <a href="//www.bizjournals.com/portland/blog/sbo/2014/11/want-to-take-a-ride-in-a-tesla-this-new.html">taxi company</a> in Portland offers rides in a Tesla.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Technology</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Amazon unveils a speaker for your home that might be <a href="//gizmodo.com/amazons-echo-might-be-its-most-important-product-in-yea-1655513291">its most important</a> product in years.</li>
<li><a href="//time.com/3563363/google-maps-redesign/">Google Maps</a> just got a redesign.</li>
<li><a href="//www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/retailandconsumer/11210817/Top-Christmas-toys-have-more-computer-power-than-Apollo-mission.html">Christmas toys have</a> âmore computer power than an Apollo mission.â</li>
<li>AppleCare for Enterprises <a href="//tcrn.ch/1tguwjY">promotes its</a> 24/7 phone support and one-hour response time.</li>
</ul>
